    "description": "Collection testing API terbaru. Flow auth saat ini: role HR tidak perlu approval (langsung approved), role Karyawan wajib approval HRD (pending -> approved/rejected). Urutan aman: 00 Health Check -> 01 Register HR -> 02 Login HR -> 03 Register Karyawan -> 04 Login Karyawan (expected pending) -> 05 Get Pending Registrations -> 06 Approve Karyawan -> 07 Login Karyawan (after approval).",
